<dl id="n52180g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n52" href="#n52180g">N52 (VI.B.42)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n52all.htm#n52180g"> 180(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Gen XI, init, </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Genesis xi: <font color="green">[1]</font> And the whole earth was of one language, and of one speech. <font color="green">[2]</font> And it came to pass, as they journeyed from the east, that they found a plain in the land of Shinar; and they dwelt there. <font color="green">[3]</font> And they said one to another, Go to, let us make brick, and burn them thoroughly. And they had brick for stone, and slime had they for mortar. <font color="green">[4]</font> And they said one to another, Go to, let us build us a city and a tower, whose top <i>may reach</i> unto heaven; and let us make us a name, lest we be scattered abroad upon the face of the whole earth. &hellip; <font color="green">[9]</font> Therefore is the name of it called Babel: because the Lord did there confound the language of all the earth. </mm> </dd></dl>
